&lt;P&gt;Megatron X:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Around the region storms started to build and rumble darkly. The &lt;BR&gt;sounds would easily obscure the sound of his engines hurtling the &lt;BR&gt;heavily armored craft forward. But soon his presense would be readily &lt;BR&gt;known. His fusion cannon and twin barrelled beam rifle began to slowly &lt;BR&gt;focus and charge their lethal energies, and for several moments the &lt;BR&gt;combined light shone brightly against the storming skies.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;But the light soon gave way to a near deafening blast. A column of &lt;BR&gt;searing energy cut across the sky, directly over the fortress. It lit &lt;BR&gt;the area brightly for nearly one full minute, and when it vanished, the &lt;BR&gt;craft responsible had arrived.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;As it descended to the battle it transformed, and now Megatron X &lt;BR&gt;surveyed the scene with distain.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;br&gt;
